      "table_notes": [
        "(1) All fees imposed and collected by and payable to McDonald's. All fees are non-refundable and uniform.",
        "(2) 5% royalty applies post-Jan 2024 for: new restaurants, McOpCo sales, ROFR exercises. 4% continues for: family transactions, new term on existing, franchisee-to-franchisee sales, rebuilds.",
        "(3) Percentage Rent 6%-23% for new/relocated traditional. Minimum 11.50% from year 8. Total change generally ≤3.50%.",
        "(4) Co-investment policy: reduce percentage rent in 0.25% increments, cost ~$30,000+ per quarter. Not required.",
        "(5) Advertising not payable to McDonald's. McOpCo companies are voting members but no controlling power.",
        "(6) Satellite rent case-by-case. MIW: 14%-15.5% of Gross Sales.",
        "(7) STO/STR percentage rent table: 9.0%-11.50%+ based on development costs.",
        "(8) BFL rent case-by-case based on personal financial net worth, projected expenses/sales.",
        "(9) Relocation contribution required if relocating.",
        "(10) Technology fees subject to periodic review and may increase.",
        "(11) One-time fees for new/existing restaurants adopting specified technology."
      ],
      "provenance": "Item 6, FDD pages 10-16, PDF pages 18-24"
    },
